OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779300668
OL,3,CMan arrested after pensioner found
OL,4,Cdead at home
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after an elderly woman was
OL,8,Ffound dead in her home.
OL,10,FRose Johnston, 68, died on Ancroft
OL,11,FRoad in Dovecot on October 4 2025.
OL,12,FMerseyside police found she had been
OL,13,Fassaulted and suffered a blunt force
OL,14,Fhead injury.
OL,16,FA 37-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
