PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779300668
OL,3,CMan arrested after pensioner found
OL,4,Cdead at home
OL,6,FPaying tribute, Rose's friend Maureen
OL,7,FJohnson said: "She was one of my best
OL,8,Fmates for 44 years. We would go out
OL,9,Ftogether, she would come to parties, I
OL,10,Fwent to her mum and dad's funerals.
OL,12,F"She was such a lovely woman, so quiet
OL,13,Fand kept herself to herself. She was a
OL,14,Fbeautiful woman. Last time I saw her
OL,15,Fproperly was at the Asda, I saw her
OL,16,Fsat outside so I sat with her and we
OL,17,Fhad a laugh.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779300668
OL,3,CMan arrested after pensioner found
OL,4,Cdead at home
OL,6,F"I said she should come round for a
OL,7,Fdrink soon and she said as long as it
OL,8,Fwasn't on a Thursday. It's so sad that
OL,9,Fwas the last time I'll speak to her."
OL,11,FRose reportedly lived in the property
OL,12,Falone following the death of her
OL,13,Fhusband.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Catherine
OL,16,FWalsh said: "Although we have made an
OL,17,Farrest our enquiries remain ongoing
OL,18,Fand it is vital that anybody with
OL,19,Finformation who hasn't already come
OL,20,Fforward does so as a matter of urgency.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779300668
OL,3,CMan arrested after pensioner found
OL,4,Cdead at home
OL,6,F"We need people to tell us about any
OL,7,Fsuspicious activity they heard or saw
OL,8,Faround the time of Rose's murder or
OL,9,Fany CCTV, dashcam or mobile phone
OL,10,Ffootage they may have or have seen
OL,11,Fwhich could assist with our
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
