OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779300668
OL,3,CMan arrested after pensioner found
OL,4,Cdead at home
OL,6,F"Rose's family have been living
OL,7,Fwithout answers for over seven months
OL,8,Fnow but we remain committed to finding
OL,9,Fthe person responsible for her death
OL,10,Fand bringing them to justice. My
OL,11,Fappeal remains with the local
OL,12,Fcommunity to come forward and tell us
OL,13,Fwhat you know."
OL,15,FIndependent organisation Crimestoppers
OL,16,Foffered a #20,000 reward in December
OL,17,Ffor information. Gary Murray, North
OL,18,FWest Regional Manager said any
OL,19,Finformation provided to the charity
OL,20,Fwould be completely anonymous.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
